Package net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.event

Events specific to components live here.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ComponentListener
    Listener interface for component events.
    ItemListener
    ItemListener listens for the selected/unselected state of items.
    PageableListener
    Defines listeners for changes to components that implement the Pageable interface.
    TreeExpansionListener
    Interface for listening to tree expansion/collapsing events.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComponentAdapter
    Empty implementation of ComponentListener for easy extending.
    ComponentEvent
    Event object for component events.
    DestroyApplicationOnClose
    Destroys an application when a component is closed.
    ItemEvent
    ItemEvent used for ItemListener events.
    PageableEvent
    Event class for Pageable events.
    TreeExpansionEvent
    Event object for tree expansion events.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ComponentEventType
    Enumeration of ComponentEvent types.
    ItemEventType
    Enumeration for ItemEvent types.
    PageableEventType
    Events type for PageableEvent.
    TreeExpansionEventType
    Tree expansion event types.
